shibboleth.actions

Class GetInfoAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • shibboleth.actions.ShibbolethAction
      • shibboleth.actions.GetInfoAction

  • public class GetInfoAction
extends ShibbolethAction
    Retrieve a Github artifact, i.e. a user, repo or contributions. Subsequenly notify listener to display this artifact. Does neither save the database nor add to the graph. Syntax: info [repo|user] -- Display info info -c [repo|user|-all] (-l) -- Retrieve and display contributions available locally, -l = all languages info -ca [repo|user] (-l) -- Retrieve and display all contributions
    Author:
    Wilco Wisse
